===Noun===
'''[[oblique]] [[case]]''' (''plural:'' '''[[oblique cases]]''')

# {{grammar}} Any noun [[case]] except the [[nominative case]] or the [[vocative case]]. The term is commonly used in [[Hindi]] grammar.

